    <body>
        <ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">
            <li>In your browser, open a new tab and go to <a href="https://www.google.com/webmasters/tools/" target="_blank">https://www.google.com/webmasters/tools/</a>.</li>
            <li>
                <p>If you do not yet have a site, click the <span class="Emphasis">Add property</span> drop-down, then select the <span class="Emphasis">Add property</span> option.</p>
                <p>If you already have a site, click the drop-down next to the site name, then select the <span class="Emphasis">Add property</span> option.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Enter the URL for your site, and click <span class="Emphasis">Continue</span>.</p>
                <p>A page opens with steps for verifying your site.</p>
            </li>
            <li>Complete the steps on the page.</li>
            <li>After you have successfully verified the site, continue with the following steps to add your sitemap.</li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>